verbose_text: Since its first detection occurred in the city of Wuhan (China) in late December 2019 the diffusion of the severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) disease, named COVID-19 (Corona Virus Disease 2019), caused by SARS-CoV-2 (officially designated by the Coronavirus Study Group of the International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses) has grown rapidly, achieving a pandemic level as declared by the WHO on March 11th.
evidence: COVID-19 (Corona Virus Disease 2019), caused by SARS-CoV-2
